---

<Layout title="Language Learning Roadmap | Christo Languages" description="Stop wasting time. Get a proven language learning system from a 10-language polyglot. Achieve fluency faster.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="text-center py-12 px-6 bg-muted/30 relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-foreground mb-6 leading-tight text-center">
        One on One Coaching
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        1:1 coaching is currently under development. Enter your email to be the first to know when it launches!
      </p>

      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto mt-8">
        <WaitlistNewsletterForm />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem / Solution Section -->
  <section id="the-problem" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Feeling Lost? Overwhelmed? Stuck?</h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        You're trying hard, but endless apps, conflicting advice, and lack of clear direction are holding you back. Sound familiar?
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-foreground text-center mb-8">The Solution: Polyglot-Guided Structure</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
      <div class="bg-card text-card-foreground border border-border p-6 rounded-lg flex flex-col hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center">
          <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span> Custom Roadmap
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base text-foreground/80">A clear, personalized plan based on your goals & learning style.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-card text-card-foreground border border-border p-6 rounded-lg flex flex-col hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center">
          <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span> Curated Resources
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base text-foreground/80">Stop searching. Get the <em>best</em> tools & materials, chosen for you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-card text-card-foreground border border-border p-6 rounded-lg flex flex-col hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-foreground mb-3 flex items-center">
          <span class="text-primary mr-2">✓</span> Efficient Strategy
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base text-foreground/80">Learn <em>how</em> to learn effectively with proven polyglot techniques.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Value Prop Section -->
  <section id="why-me" class="py-12 px-6 bg-muted/30 border-y border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Why Trust My Guidance?</h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-accent font-medium mb-6">I've Successfully Learned 10 Languages.</p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-foreground/80 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Forget generic advice. Get actionable strategies refined through real-world mastery. I'll help you avoid common pitfalls, save countless hours, and build a system for consistent progress.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-card text-card-foreground border border-border p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <p class="text-base text-foreground/80 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2 text-xl font-semibold font-serif">✓</span> Save Time & Energy
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card text-card-foreground border border-border p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <p class="text-base text-foreground/80 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2 text-xl font-semibold font-serif">✓</span> Avoid Costly Mistakes
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card text-card-foreground border border-border p-6 rounded-lg hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300">
          <p class="text-base text-foreground/80 flex items-center">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2 text-xl font-semibold font-serif">✓</span> Follow a Proven Path
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>